title: Gilbert Road Race
course: roughly 9 mile/lap road race on county roads south and west of Gilbert Iowa.  Center line rule in place.
directions: From I-35, exit on 13th St in Ames.  Go west on 13th to Hwy 69 (Grand Ave) Go north about 5 miles and turn left at the Casey\'s on 170th Ave (E29).  The elementary school is to the left at THE stop sign.
